title: An asymmetrically coordinated ZnCoFe hetero-trimetallic atom catalyst enhances the electrocatalytic oxygen reaction
content:
Energy Environ. Sci., 2024, 17,2298-2308
DOI: 10.1039/D4EE00134F, Paper
Changli Chen, Jing Chai, Mengru Sun, Tianqi Guo, Jie Lin, Yurong Zhou, Zhiyi Sun, Fang Zhang, Liang Zhang, Wenxing Chen, Yujing Li
In this work, we design an asymmetric hetero-trimetallic single-atom catalyst with ZnN3CoN3FeN2S active catalytic sites to enhance the oxygen reaction performances.
